{"tid":1800241,"cid":27,"subCid":0,"title":"大家重記唔記得天水圍中彈既手足","createTime":"2019-12-27T15:17:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-03T13:42:34.000Z","uid":169400,"like":95,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":48,"replies":[{"pid":"2ddfa8eccc4e5858d307839fe00d948d784c2462","tid":1800241,"uid":169400,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T15:17:58.000Z","msg":"101<br />\n1111<br />\n天水圍中彈學生<br />\n陳同學同周同學<br />\n重有好多數唔曬既手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家重記唔記得佢地付出左幾多青春同代價，班細路犧牲左咁多係前面幫你地擋。係時候候野啦，雖然最近嘅文宣少咗好多，不過我哋仲有時間不停咁AirDrop呢張圖出去啦。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而且個集會有不反，集會地點重要係黃到發金既天水圍舉行，唔洗驚有藍絲同鄉黑黎搞事。約定大家聽晚銀座見！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n元朗區中學生集會- 延續革命 毋忘初心<br />\n(聯署721 滅不了的連儂牆聲音 學生抗爭心聲) <br />\n日期 : 12月28日 (六)<br />\n時間：19:30-21:30<br />\n地點：天水圍 銀座<br />\n自備：memo紙<br />\n✅已獲發不反對通知書<br />\n公海：<a href=\"http://t.me/joinchat/KwqxNxX0iDxH4rGWczmIA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FKwqxNxX0iDxH4rGWczmIA&d=CRZj9ITMXIzKHLmvffUzPGhNlLB%2BLbsdBqu6cuXqlDc%3D&h=93c0b25f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/joinchat/KwqxNxX0iDxH4rGWczmIA</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mQB4nUj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmQB4nUj.png&h=35333038&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"234260cd0e69d0334c317e86e3deb2cbc80f193f","tid":1800241,"uid":180114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T15:19:29.000Z","msg":"甴近平"},{